title: 091 - Could You Beat Up A Kangaroo?
description: On today's show, the boys discuss everyone looking into buying a house and Nick officially moving into his new house this weekend. Plus the guys dive into a loaded Pod FOD where they chat about whether or not they could beat up a kangaroo, Dexter coming back for 10 more episodes, which character of The Office the guys would pick to be their teammate on The Amazing Race, if the guys would be willing to try and take down a mixture of a shark and rhino for $5,000,000, they check in with the Booby Brotherz from DAHN undah, plus much more, and Nick ends the episode with another edition of Friday Bangerz to help send you into a great weekend. Send in your questions to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram to be featured on the show. We appreciate you all for listening, enjoy.
